Youssef Ben Hayoun Sadafi (Arabic) a mụrụ (22 Disemba 1990-) na Agadir bụ onye mba Moroccan na-eme ihe nkiri, ihe nlereanya na onye agha
Ọ ghọrọ onye a ma ama site na usoro TV Thousand and One Nights na Medi 1 TV na-arụ ọrụ "Farès", ma mesịa n'oge ọ na-ekere òkè na Arab casting, ihe ngosi nkà Arabic.
A mụrụ ya na Agadir nke nna Morocco na nne Italian, Ben Hayoun Sadafi tolitere na Marrakesh, tupu ọ gaa Ịtali iji mụọ ihe mgbe ọ dị afọ 18.
Ben Hayoun Sadafi malitere ọrụ n'ime ihe ngosi mgbe ọ fọrọ nke nta ka ọ bụrụ afọ iri abụọ
Ọ pụtara na mkpọsa n'esise foto  maka ụdị dịka Johnnie Walker na Wings of Freedom na mgbakwunye na foto maka Ministry of Tourism iji kwalite njem nleta n'ime ụlọ na Russia.
Oge mbụ Ben Hayoun Sadafi pụtara na Moroccan TV, bụ dịka "Farès" na usoro Moroccan "1001 Nights" n'afọ 2011
O sonyekwara na Arab Casting, ihe ngosi nkà nke a na-egosi na Abu Dhabi TV "Chorouq", ma jee ozi dịka onye nche Nabila Benatia n'oge a na-agbapụ ihe nkiri TV Allo Nabila na Marrakech.
O nwere ọrụ bụ isi na Inwi action webseries #code, nke malitere na 1 June 2017.

Ben Hayoun Sadafi malitere martial arts mgbe ọ dị afọ 4, malite na taekwando ma gaa n'ihu na kickboxing mgbe ọ dị dingwaga 12 ma mesịa, Brazilian jiu-jitsu. N'afọ 2012, o ritere ihe nrite ọla edo na Brazilian jiu-jitsu na Morocco na Tunisia
